    "short_description": {
        "value": "EarthGPT is a universal multi-modal large language model (MLLM) for multi-sensor image comprehension in the remote sensing (RS) domain. It unifies various RS interpretation tasks (scene classification, image captioning, region-level captioning, VQA, visual grounding, object detection, etc.) and supports multi-sensor images (optical, SAR, infrared) via a visual-enhanced perception mechanism, cross-modal mutual comprehension, and unified instruction tuning. It is trained on the MMRS-1M dataset (over 1M image-text pairs from 34 RS datasets).",
        "confidence": 0.8242
    },
